      <t>This document describes Segment Routing Mapped to IPv6 (SRm6). SRm6 is a Segment Routing (SR) solution that supports a wide variety of use-cases while complying with IPv6 specifications. SRm6 is optimized for ASIC-based routers that operate at high data rates.</t>
